pan></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >描述：对游戏结果的持久化存储。实现了对数据库的增、改、读操作。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >注：</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >sdk<font face=\"宋体\" >的版本不宜过高。本次程序实现，采用的是</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >S</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >DK</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >-version<font face=\"宋体\" >为</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >8</font><font face=\"宋体\" >。如果采用</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >S</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >DK</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >-version<font face=\"宋体\" >为</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >15</font><font face=\"宋体\" >将会报错。</font></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style=\"text-align:center;\" ><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >3.3<font face=\"宋体\" >修改的功能模块和遇到的问题，原因分析，处理结果</font></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >完成的修改功能模块序号：<font face=\"Times New Roman\" >1</font><font face=\"宋体\" >、</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >2</font><font face=\"宋体\" >、</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >3</font><font face=\"宋体\" >、</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >5</font></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;\" ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >EX:</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;\" ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >【问题一】</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >当前<font face=\"Times New Roman\" >jsoup</font><font face=\"宋体\" >读取的是学校的&#8220;</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >学校要闻</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >&#8221;栏目内容，请读取&#8220;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >焦点资讯</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >&#8221;栏目的内容。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >【解决方法】</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >修改<font face=\"Times New Roman\" >url</font><font face=\"宋体\" >地址即可实现解析&#8220;焦点资讯&#8220;栏目的内容</font></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style=\"text-align:center;\" ><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style=\"text-align:center;\" ><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style=\"text-align:center;\" ><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;\" ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >【问题二】</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >资源里面有一个原始<font face=\"Times New Roman\" >xml</font><font face=\"宋体\" >文件记录了开发者的信息，请修改为自己的信息。然后通过点击&#8220;</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >home_btn2</font><font face=\"宋体\" >&#8221;按钮读取</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\" >xml</font><font face=\"宋体\" >信息并展示出来</font></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >【解决方法】</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\" >创建</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-siz